rname/astro-darkness",[19,20,21,22],"astro","three.js","dark-theme","animations",true,"The theme you're currently viewing! Darkness is an experimental Astro theme that pushes the boundaries of web animation and dark design.\n\n## Features\n\n- 5000 Three.js particles in 3D space\n- Custom cursor with hover effects\n- Glitch text animations\n- View Transitions API\n- Full TypeScript support\n- Blog and portfolio system\n\n## Tech Stack\n\nBuilt with modern web technologies for optimal performance and developer experience.","src/content/projects/darkness-theme.md","9711671c2a73b526",{"html":28,"metadata":29},"\u003Cp>The theme you’re currently viewing! Darkness is an experimental Astro theme that pushes the boundaries of web animation and dark design.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"features\">Features\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>5000 Three.js particles in 3D space\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Custom cursor with hover effects\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Glitch text animations\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>View Transitions API\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Full TypeScript support\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Blog and portfolio system\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"tech-stack\">Tech Stack\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Built with modern web technologies for optimal performance and developer experience.\u003C/p>",{"headings":30,"localImagePaths":38,"remoteImagePaths":39,"frontmatter":40,"imagePaths":42},[31,35],{"depth":32,"slug":33,"text":34},2,"features","Features",{"depth":32,"slug":36,"text":37},"tech-stack","Tech Stack",[],[],{"title":14,"description":15,"image":16,"github":17,"tags":41,"featured":23},[19,20,21,22],[],"particle-playground",{"id":43,"data":45,"body":51,"filePath":52,"digest":53,"rendered":54},{"title":46,"description":47,"tags":48,"featured":23},"Particle Playground","Interactive Three.js particle system with customizable parameters",[20,49,50],"webgl","interactive","An interactive playground for experimenting with Three.js particle systems. Adjust particle count, colors, speed, and behavior in real-time.\n\n## Highlights\n\n- Real-time parameter adjustment\n- Multiple particle behaviors\n- Color palette customization\n- Export configurations","src/content/projects/particle-playground.md","7ca9257303db4c80",{"html":55,"metadata":56},"\u003Cp>An interactive playground for experimenting with Three.js particle systems. Adjust particle count, colors, speed, and behavior in real-time.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"highlights\">Highlights\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Real-time parameter adjustment\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Multiple particle behaviors\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Color palette customization\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Export configurations\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>",{"headings":57,"localImagePaths":61,"remoteImagePaths":62,"frontmatter":63,"imagePaths":65},[58],{"depth":32,"slug":59,"text":60},"highlights","Highlights",[],[],{"title":46,"description":47,"tags":64,"featured":23},[20,49,50],[],"blog",["Map",68,69,100,101,136,137],"welcome-to-darkness",{"id":68,"data":70,"body":75,"filePath":76,"digest":77,"rendered":78},{"title":71,"description":72,"pubDate":73,"tags":74},"Welcome to the Darkness","Exploring the depths of dark-themed web design with Three.js and modern animations",["Date","2025-12-15T00:00:00.000Z"],[19,20,21,22],"# Welcome to the Darkness\n\nThis is the first post on my new dark-themed blog. Built with Astro and powered by intense animations, this blog explores the intersection of design and motion.\n\n## What Makes This Theme Special?\n\nThe Darkness theme pushes the boundaries of web animation:\n\n- **5000 Three.js particles** creating an immersive 3D background\n- **Glitch effects** that bring cyberpunk aesthetics to life\n- **Custom cursor** that responds to your every move\n- **View Transitions** for buttery smooth page navigation\n\n## The Technology\n\nThis theme is built on cutting-edge web technologies:\n\n```javascript\n// Example: Creating particles in Three.js\nconst particlesGeometry = new THREE.BufferGeometry();\nconst particlesCount = 5000;\nconst posArray = new Float32Array(particlesCount * 3);\n\nfor (let i = 0; i \u003C particlesCount * 3; i += 3) {\n  posArray[i] = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 100;\n  posArray[i + 1] = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 100;\n  posArray[i + 2] = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 100;\n}\n```\n\n## Motion and Beauty\n\nEvery element on this site is designed to move. From the floating background shapes to the pulsing glow effects, motion is at the core of the experience.\n\nStay tuned for more posts about web animation, Three.js techniques, and dark design patterns!","src/content/blog/welcome-to-darkness.md","6827776dea5b8fa5",{"html":79,"metadata":80},"\u003Ch1 id=\"welcome-to-the-darkness\">Welcome to the Darkness\u003C/h1>\n\u003Cp>This is the first post on my new dark-themed blog. Built with Astro and powered by intense animations, this blog explores the intersection of design and motion.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"what-makes-this-theme-special\">What Makes This Theme Special?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>The Darkness theme pushes the boundaries of web animation:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>5000 Three.js particles\u003C/strong> creating an immersive 3D background\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Glitch effects\u003C/strong> that bring cyberpunk aesthetics to life\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Custom cursor\u003C/strong> that responds to your every move\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>View Transitions\u003C/strong> for buttery smooth page navigation\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"the-technology\">The Technology\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>This theme is built on cutting-edge web technologies:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#6A737D\">// Example: Creating particles in Three.js\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">const\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> particlesGeometry\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> =\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> new\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> THREE\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">BufferGeometry\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">();\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">const\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> particlesCount\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> =\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 5000\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">const\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> posArray\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> =\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> new\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\"> Float32Array\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(particlesCount \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">*\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">);\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">for\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> (\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">let\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">; i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">&#x3C;\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> particlesCount \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">*\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">; i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">+=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">) {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  posArray[i] \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> (Math.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">random\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">() \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">-\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0.5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">) \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">*\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 100\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  posArray[i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">+\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">] \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> (Math.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">random\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">() \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">-\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0.5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">) \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">*\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 100\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  posArray[i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">+\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">] \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> (Math.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">random\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">() \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">-\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0.5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">) \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">*\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 100\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">}\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"motion-and-beauty\">Motion and Beauty\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Every element on this site is designed to move. From the floating background shapes to the pulsing glow effects, motion is at the core of the experience.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Stay tuned for more posts about web animation, Three.js techniques, and dark design patterns!\u003C/p>",{"headings":81,"localImagePaths":94,"remoteImagePaths":95,"frontmatter":96,"imagePaths":99},[82,85,88,91],{"depth":83,"slug":84,"text":71},1,"welcome-to-the-darkness",{"depth":32,"slug":86,"text":87},"what-makes-this-theme-special","What Makes This Theme Special?",{"depth":32,"slug":89,"text":90},"the-technology","The Technology",{"depth":32,"slug":92,"text":93},"motion-and-beauty","Motion and Beauty",[],[],{"title":71,"description":72,"pubDate":97,"tags":98},["Date","2025-12-15T00:00:00.000Z"],[19,20,21,22],[],"css-animations-mastery",{"id":100,"data":102,"body":109,"filePath":110,"digest":111,"rendered":112},{"title":103,"description":104,"pubDate":105,"tags":106},"Mastering CSS Animations in Dark Themes","Advanced CSS animation techniques for creating motion-rich dark interfaces",["Date","2025-12-25T00:00:00.000Z"],[107,22,108,21],"css","design","# Mastering CSS Animations in Dark Themes\n\nCSS animations are the backbone of any motion-rich interface. In dark themes, they become even more powerful when combined with glows, shadows, and gradients.\n\n## The Float Animation\n\nOne of the most elegant effects is the subtle float:\n\n```css\n@keyframes float {\n  0%, 100% {\n    transform: translateY(0px);\n  }\n  50% {\n    transform: translateY(-20px);\n  }\n}\n\n.element {\n  animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n```\n\n## Glow Effects\n\nIn dark themes, glow effects create depth:\n\n```css\n@keyframes pulse-glow {\n  0%, 100% {\n    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);\n  }\n  50% {\n    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.6);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Gradient Animations\n\nAnimated gradients bring backgrounds to life:\n\n```css\n.shimmer-text {\n  background: linear-gradient(\n    90deg,\n    var(--color-accent-purple),\n    var(--color-accent-pink),\n    var(--color-accent-blue),\n    var(--color-accent-purple)\n  );\n  background-size: 200% auto;\n  background-clip: text;\n  -webkit-background-clip: text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n  animation: text-shimmer 3s linear infinite;\n}\n\n@keyframes text-shimmer {\n  to {\n    background-position: 200% center;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Performance Considerations\n\n- Use `transform` and `opacity` for best performance\n- Avoid animating `width`, `height`, or `margin`\n- Use `will-change` sparingly\n- Test on low-end devices\n\nThe key to great dark theme animations is subtlety combined with impact. Use motion to guide the eye, not distract it.","src/content/blog/css-animations-mastery.md","a8331cf6aff0ab07",{"html":113,"metadata":114},"\u003Ch1 id=\"mastering-css-animations-in-dark-themes\">Mastering CSS Animations in Dark Themes\u003C/h1>\n\u003Cp>CSS animations are the backbone of any motion-rich interface. In dark themes, they become even more powerful when combined with glows, shadows, and gradients.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"the-float-animation\">The Float Animation\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>One of the most elegant effects is the subtle float:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"css\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">@keyframes\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#FFAB70\"> float\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">  0%\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">, \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">100%\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    transform\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">translateY\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">0\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">px\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">);\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  }\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">  50%\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    transform\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">translateY\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">-20\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">px\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">);\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  }\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">}\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">.element\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">  animation\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: float \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">s\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> ease-in-out\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> infinite\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">}\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"glow-effects\">Glow Effects\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>In dark themes, glow effects create depth:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"css\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">@keyframes\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#FFAB70\"> pulse-glow\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">  0%\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">, \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">100%\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    box-shadow\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">0\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 20\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">px\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> rgba\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">168\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">, \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">85\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">, \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">247\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">, \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">0.3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">);\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  }\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">  50%\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    box-shadow\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">0\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 40\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">px\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> rgba\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">168\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">, \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">85\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">, \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">247\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">, \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">0.6\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">);\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  }\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">}\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"gradient-animations\">Gradient Animations\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Animated gradients bring backgrounds to life:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"css\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">.shimmer-text\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">  background\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">linear-gradient\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    90\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">deg\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">,\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    var\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#FFAB70\">--color-accent-purple\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">),\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    var\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#FFAB70\">--color-accent-pink\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">),\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    var\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#FFAB70\">--color-accent-blue\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">),\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    var\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#FFAB70\">--color-accent-purple\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">)\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  );\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">  background-size\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">200\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">%\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> auto\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">  background-clip\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">text\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">  -webkit-background-clip\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">text\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">  -webkit-text-fill-color\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">transparent\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">  animation\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: text-shimmer \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">s\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> linear\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> infinite\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">}\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">@keyframes\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#FFAB70\"> text-shimmer\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">  to\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    background-position\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">200\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">%\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> center\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  }\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">}\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"performance-considerations\">Performance Considerations\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Use \u003Ccode>transform\u003C/code> and \u003Ccode>opacity\u003C/code> for best performance\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Avoid animating \u003Ccode>width\u003C/code>, \u003Ccode>height\u003C/code>, or \u003Ccode>margin\u003C/code>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Use \u003Ccode>will-change\u003C/code> sparingly\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Test on low-end devices\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>The key to great dark theme animations is subtlety combined with impact. Use motion to guide the eye, not distract it.\u003C/p>",{"headings":115,"localImagePaths":130,"remoteImagePaths":131,"frontmatter":132,"imagePaths":135},[116,118,121,124,127],{"depth":83,"slug":117,"text":103},"mastering-css-animations-in-dark-themes",{"depth":32,"slug":119,"text":120},"the-float-animation","The Float Animation",{"depth":32,"slug":122,"text":123},"glow-effects","Glow Effects",{"depth":32,"slug":125,"text":126},"gradient-animations","Gradient Animations",{"depth":32,"slug":128,"text":129},"performance-considerations","Performance Considerations",[],[],{"title":103,"description":104,"pubDate":133,"tags":134},["Date","2025-12-25T00:00:00.000Z"],[107,22,108,21],[],"threejs-particle-systems",{"id":136,"data":138,"body":145,"filePath":146,"digest":147,"rendered":148},{"title":139,"description":140,"pubDate":141,"tags":142},"Building Particle Systems with Three.js","A deep dive into creating beautiful particle effects for web backgrounds",["Date","2025-12-20T00:00:00.000Z"],[20,49,143,144],"particles","tutorial","# Building Particle Systems with Three.js\n\nParticle systems are one of the most visually striking effects you can add to a website. Let's explore how to create them using Three.js.\n\n## The Basics\n\nA particle system consists of many small elements (particles) that move and behave according to specific rules. In Three.js, we use `Points` geometry for optimal performance.\n\n## Setting Up\n\nFirst, create a geometry to hold particle positions:\n\n```javascript\nconst particlesGeometry = new THREE.BufferGeometry();\nconst particlesCount = 5000;\n```\n\n## Adding Color\n\nParticles become more interesting with varied colors:\n\n```javascript\nconst colorArray = new Float32Array(particlesCount * 3);\n\nfor (let i = 0; i \u003C particlesCount * 3; i += 3) {\n  const colorType = Math.random();\n  if (colorType \u003C 0.33) {\n    // Purple\n    colorArray[i] = 0.66;\n    colorArray[i + 1] = 0.33;\n    colorArray[i + 2] = 0.97;\n  } else if (colorType \u003C 0.66) {\n    // Pink\n    colorArray[i] = 0.93;\n    colorArray[i + 1] = 0.28;\n    colorArray[i + 2] = 0.60;\n  } else {\n    // Blue\n    colorArray[i] = 0.23;\n    colorArray[i + 1] = 0.51;\n    colorArray[i + 2] = 0.96;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Animation\n\nThe magic happens in the animation loop:\n\n```javascript\nfunction animate() {\n  requestAnimationFrame(animate);\n\n  particlesMesh.rotation.y += 0.001;\n  particlesMesh.rotation.x = Math.sin(time) * 0.1;\n\n  renderer.render(scene, camera);\n}\n```\n\n## Performance Tips\n\n- Limit particle count for mobile devices\n- Use `AdditiveBlending` for glowing effects\n- Consider using instanced meshes for very large systems\n\nHappy coding in the darkness! 🌌","src/content/blog/threejs-particle-systems.md","8c52c7b89b09b8a9",{"html":149,"metadata":150},"\u003Ch1 id=\"building-particle-systems-with-threejs\">Building Particle Systems with Three.js\u003C/h1>\n\u003Cp>Particle systems are one of the most visually striking effects you can add to a website. Let’s explore how to create them using Three.js.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"the-basics\">The Basics\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>A particle system consists of many small elements (particles) that move and behave according to specific rules. In Three.js, we use \u003Ccode>Points\u003C/code> geometry for optimal performance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"setting-up\">Setting Up\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>First, create a geometry to hold particle positions:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">const\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> particlesGeometry\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> =\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> new\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> THREE\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">BufferGeometry\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">();\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">const\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> particlesCount\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> =\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 5000\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"adding-color\">Adding Color\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Particles become more interesting with varied colors:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">const\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> colorArray\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> =\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> new\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\"> Float32Array\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(particlesCount \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">*\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">);\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">for\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> (\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">let\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">; i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">&#x3C;\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> particlesCount \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">*\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">; i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">+=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">) {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">  const\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> colorType\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> =\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> Math.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">random\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">();\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">  if\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> (colorType \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">&#x3C;\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0.33\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">) {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#6A737D\">    // Purple\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">    colorArray[i] \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0.66\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">    colorArray[i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">+\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">] \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0.33\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">    colorArray[i \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">+\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">] \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">=\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> 0.97\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">  } \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"